           SHORT="PKCS#11 wrapper library"

cat << EOF
PKCS#11 wrapper library.

This code repository produces two libraries:

    libp11 provides a higher-level (compared to the PKCS#11 library) interface
    to access PKCS#11 objects. It is designed to integrate with applications
    that use OpenSSL. pkcs11 engine plugin for the OpenSSL library allows
    accessing PKCS#11 modules in a semi-transparent way.

The wiki page for this project is at https://github.com/OpenSC/libp11/wiki and
includes a bug tracker and source browser.
EOF
